Show me your hands!

1056
01:20:26.343 --> 01:20:28.083
I did it.

1057
01:20:28.084 --> 01:20:30.259
- What?
- I did it. It was me.

1058
01:20:30.260 --> 01:20:31.869
It was...

1059
01:20:31.870 --> 01:20:34.263
It was all me.

1060
01:20:34.264 --> 01:20:36.743
I did everything.

1061
01:20:36.744 --> 01:20:37.833
Bomb!

1062
01:20:39.138 --> 01:20:40.965
